{"tid":2012164,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"舞台劇《炎炎消防隊》全員照公開","createTime":"2020-05-11T12:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T16:03:40.000Z","uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd8e39fa5a0b4b52bcc1547e577ad8a1051ba64","tid":2012164,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J3a4Jq0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ3a4Jq0.jpg&h=bc4a1328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yYU5Ek.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yYU5Ek.jpg&h=6163c554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/meZ1LEm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmeZ1LEm.jpg&h=1980105a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《炎炎消防隊》是大久保篤於週刊少年Magazine上連載的少年漫畫(台灣由東立出版社代理)。2019年推出動畫，預定2020年7月改編成舞台劇。<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n森羅日下部：牧島輝<br />\nアーサー・ボイル：小澤廉<br />\n秋樽桜備：君沢ユウキ <br />\n武久火縄：馬場良馬<br />\n茉希尾瀬：星波 <br />\nアイリス：礒部花凜<br />\n烈火星宮：小南光司 <br />\nカリム・フラム：校條拳太朗<br />\nフォイェン・リィ：安里勇哉<br />\n環古達：早乙女ゆう <br />\nレオナルド・バーンズ：萩野崇<br />\n象日下部：木津つばさ <br />\nプリンセス 火華ヒバナ：野本ほたる <br />\nジョーカー：和泉宗兵"},{"pid":"afc4cb03873b664453455684f7e643bfa1abe0a0","tid":2012164,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"555014decd3d8ead028adcd9c843a900539c98f8","tid":2012164,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime